name: Belinda
description: I am a person who never hides my feelings, I believe it is very important to express our feelings to our close ones and to show that we value what and whom we have in our life. People recognize me by my smile, yes, I am life loving and positive person, I am sociable and always see the best in people. Feeling boring or pessimistic is not for me, I cannot accept when people say that it is not possible, it is so hard, I don’t want to do this or that. I prefer to enjoy life and to act. I am a home person. It would be nice to try something extreme, maybe with my special one, I would like to try parachute jumping…
